@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_onnlnn(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (0.88 / wp.abs((v1 + 0.48 + tmp + 0.04)))
    tmp = ((wp.exp(v2 + 0.47) + 0.46) * wp.sin((v0 + 0.31 - v0 + 0.50)))
    v0 = (0.64 - wp.abs((tmp + 0.08 * v1 + 0.40)))
    data[tid] = v0
